collections.name: Flashy Dark Monsters
collections.description: Flashy Dark Monster that I created bright and colorful illustrations of scary monsters that everyone fears and dislikes. Despite their intimidating appearance, these monsters have a certain charm or cuteness hidden beneath the surface. Each character is designed to be both frightening and endearing, balancing their dark nature with playful, eye-catching details. Their exaggerated expressions and unique features add a whimsical twist, making them more approachable. Through these designs, I aimed to show that even scary or misunderstood creatures can have a softer, more lovable side if you take a closer look.
